Html:
Hi Team,

I am very new to PHPExcel, Like to know this script supports importing the excel sheet data to a mysql.

Please guide me.

Arvind

Have you looked at any of the documentation yet, particularly the Reade documentation?

PHPExcel won't write a spreadsheet to a database for you; but it will let you write a script that reads the file, loop through each row of each worksheet, and build an SQL insert statement from the cell data that you can then insert into your database
